EIP-2537 tests for Prague PR: https://github.com/ethereum/execution-spec-tests/pull/499
Compiled fixtures here: ~~https://github.com/ethereum/execution-spec-tests/files/14998309/fixtures_develop.tar.gz~~ https://github.com/ethereum/execution-spec-tests/files/15099569/fixtures_develop.tar.gz

The fixtures do _not_ contain any other EIP for Prague, and therefore could fail on clients that do implement other EIPs in the same branch.
